=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 31, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vcf1665702584675.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vcf1665702584675.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vcf1665702584675.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vcf1665702584675\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      TextArea\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The TextArea DSP widget represents a field as a multi-line field containing plain\n      text. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__section_w2136ab1b5b1_w2137ab1b5_w2138ab1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__fig_bhz_hft_dhc\">\n<p class=\"p\">Static Text Area Widget in Chrome</p>\n<img alt=\"Static Text Area Widget in Chrome\" class=\"image\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__image_o1s_kft_dhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Static-Text-Area-Widget-in-Chrome.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__table_d13766e1_d13767e1_d13768e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Summary</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Logical Widget Name:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n EditBox\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Maps to Physical Widget :\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vht1718381378389.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vht1718381378389.html\" title=\"The htmltextarea DSP widget defines the properties of a &lt;textarea&gt; input control in a Dynamic Server Page. This is used to represent a field as a multi-line field containing plain text.\">htmltextarea</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default definition:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TextArea=htmltextarea(detail=dblclick)</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Supported triggers:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__li_d43814e1_d43815e1_d43816e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bqj1665702585000.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bqj1665702585000.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to an interactive event on a field or entity widget, such as the user clicking on the field.\">trigger detail</a>—executed on double-click.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__li_d43817e1_d43818e1_d43819e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oyb1665702587872.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oyb1665702587872.html\" title=\"This web trigger is used to program behavior when the DSP widget loses focus.\">webtrigger onBlur</a>—executed when widget loses focus.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__li_d43820e1_d43821e1_d43822e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pwu1665702589985.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pwu1665702589985.html\" title=\"Use this trigger to program behavior when data in the DSP widget is interactively changed by the user. The trigger is not activated when data is changed by the Uniface JavaScript API.\">webtrigger OnChange</a>—executed when user changes value.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__li_d43823e1_d43824e1_d43825e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dcx1665702590735.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dcx1665702590735.html\" title=\"The onSyntaxError web trigger is activated when a field syntax violation is detected in the browser. It can be used to customize or override the default syntax error handling.\">webtrigger onSyntaxError</a>—executed in response to the OnChange event in browser.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__li_d43826e1_d43827e1_d43828e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uuy1665702590810.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uuy1665702590810.html\" title=\"The onSyntaxErrorResolved web trigger is used to customize behavior when a field syntax error has been corrected.\">webtrigger onSyntaxErrorResolved</a>—executed in response to the OnChange event in browser.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Supported properties:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n See <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vht1718381378389.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vht1718381378389.html\" title=\"The htmltextarea DSP widget defines the properties of a &lt;textarea&gt; input control in a Dynamic Server Page. This is used to represent a field as a multi-line field containing plain text.\">htmltextarea</a>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Use for:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Fields of any Uniface Data Type except\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">Image</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__section_w2139ab1b5b3_w2140ab1b5_w2141ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d300274e228\">\n                       \n Widget Property Restrictions\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__p_d114326e1_d114327e1_d114328e1\">The following restrictions apply:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vcf1665702584675__li_d43829e1_d43830e1_d43831e1\">For the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Text Alignment</span> (<code class=\"ph codeph\">style:text-decoration</code>) property, the value <code class=\"ph codeph\">blink</code> is not supported.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532951\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532951\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "TextArea Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 31, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 TextArea The TextArea DSP widget represents a field as a multi-line field containing plain text. Static Text Area Widget in Chrome Table 1. Widget Summary Logical Widget Name: EditBox Maps to Physical Widget : htmltextarea Default definition: TextArea=htmltextarea(detail=dblclick) Supported triggers: trigger detail —executed on double-click. webtrigger onBlur —executed when widget loses focus. webtrigger OnChange —executed when user changes value. webtrigger onSyntaxError —executed in response to the OnChange event in browser. webtrigger onSyntaxErrorResolved —executed in response to the OnChange event in browser. Supported properties: See htmltextarea . Use for: Fields of any Uniface Data Type except Image . Widget Property Restrictions The following restrictions apply: For the Text Alignment ( style:text-decoration ) property, the value blink is not supported. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}